<p>John and Dave are back after their schedule hiccup last week due to Hurricane Irene, and they&rsquo;ve got a whirlwind show for you all today! Lots of great questions came in over the past couple of weeks, including controlling Lion&rsquo;s desktop order, moving from Aperture to iPhoto, diagnosing Apple Mail.app problems, resolving iOS app quirks, and much, much more. Listen today (it&rsquo;s free!) and enjoy learning from your two favorite geeks.</p>
